Should I just lick it off the counter, then?

1001
01:17:13,979 --> 01:17:15,241
- Oh, no!
- Yeah.

1002
01:17:15,414 --> 01:17:18,474
Sorry, no... It's been a long time
since I've seen a man that naked.

1003
01:17:18,650 --> 01:17:22,177
I mean, you have a...
How about that drink?

1004
01:17:22,721 --> 01:17:25,484
- You're very sweet.
- Oh, God.

1005
01:17:25,656 --> 01:17:29,057
