1045
01:20:32,031 --> 01:20:34,295
I was in Gerry's band.

1046
01:20:34,467 --> 01:20:36,594
Not Billy...

1047
01:20:36,769 --> 01:20:38,031
...Gallagher?
- One and the same.

1048
01:20:39,772 --> 01:20:41,797
It's... It's all right.

1049
01:20:41,975 --> 01:20:44,341
It's all right. Me and Gerry,
we shared everything together.

1050
01:20:45,945 --> 01:20:48,879
Oh, no, no, no, I didn't mean it like that.

1051
01:20:49,047 --> 01:20:52,244
What I meant was, you know,
he wouldn't have a problem...

1052
01:20:53,519 --> 01:20:55,612
Well, he might have a problem
but, you know...

1053
01:20:55,787 --> 01:20:58,654
...there's not much
he can do about it now, is there?

1054
01:21:00,826 --> 01:21:02,384
Holly.

1055
01:21:03,362 --> 01:21:06,387
Come here. Come back to bed.

1056
01:21:07,431 --> 01:21:09,729
Now, let's... Let's talk.

1057
01:21:12,803 --> 01:21:14,270
Oh...

1058
01:21:14,572 --> 01:21:16,733
I heard he died.

1059
01:21:18,676 --> 01:21:21,873
Tumor, was it? Yeah.

1060
01:21:22,646 --> 01:21:25,911
You know, Gerry and I, we...

1061
01:21:26,082 --> 01:21:29,916
