1071
01:22:06,955 --> 01:22:08,354
Yeah?

1072
01:22:08,823 --> 01:22:11,951
Okay, here you go. Come on, sit back.

1073
01:22:16,763 --> 01:22:18,560
You know, he was...

1074
01:22:18,732 --> 01:22:21,166
