1168
01:29:09,418 --> 01:29:11,409
<i>At first, the no-talking thing didn't last.</i>

1169
01:29:11,587 --> 01:29:13,452
<i>Before long, I couldn't get you to shut up.</i>

1170
01:29:13,622 --> 01:29:20,117
<i>But you were so cute, trying to impress me
